7). 44. Rabalais G, Adams G, Stover B. PPD skin test conversion in health-care workers after exposure to Mycobacterium tuberculosis infection in infants [Letter]. Lancet 1991;338:826. 45. Wallgren A. On contagiousness of childhood tuberculosis. Acta Pediatr Scand 1937;22: 229&hyph;34. 46. Riley RL. Airborne infection. Am J Med 1974;57:466&hyph;75.
